window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The last of her kind. Four hot alpha mates. A legacy of bloodshed.</b></p> <p>When Ren Landis goes looking for excitement on her 21st birthday, getting kidnapped is a little more than she bargained for. So is finding out that shifters exist - and that she's one, too. As the last of the dragon shifters, she's got a role to fulfill: Take the alphas of the four shifter groups as her mates and unite all shifter kind. No pressure, right?</p> <p>Too bad Ren's fate isn't as simple as getting it on with four scorching-hot men. A group of rogues is out for dragon-shifter blood, intent on finishing the massacre they started years ago. With deceitful fae and murderous vampires thrown into the mix, the paranormal world is on the verge of catastrophe.</p> <p>How can a girl who's only known she's a shifter for a week heal 16 years of chaos?</p> <p><b>Contains mature themes.</b></p>"; 
